  <description><![CDATA[<p>Walk the <a data-udi="umb://document/f13578bcd0ea422bb13fbbbc34693d47" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f13578bcd0ea422bb13fbbbc34693d47}" title="Amalfi Coast">Amalfi Coast</a>, following some of the most picturesque trails in the world! On this three-night trip you’ll be guided along clifftop paths, soaking up the spectacular coastal scenes and exploring villages along the way. We all know walking works up an appetite – you’ll find yourself in the best place for trying tasty local food. So we’ve included some snack stops to keep those energy levels up – try local cakes, have a traditional <a data-udi="umb://document/7e6d84fc86844d12b8c73851f2035fb1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/7e6d84fc86844d12b8c73851f2035fb1}" title="Neapolitan Riviera">Neapolitan</a> lunch and taste regions famous limoncello!</p>
<p>You’ll be in safe hands with the help of our local guides – they know these routes inside out. They’ll take you along the mule tracks that connect the Amalfi villages and teach you the regions legends as you walk along the ‘Lemon Path’ and the ‘Path of the Gods’ from Bomerano to the colourful village of Positano. </p>
<div>
<h2 style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/amalfi-coast-walkingt#Tour highlights">Tour highlights</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/amalfi-coast-walking#Itinerary&quot;">Itinerary</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/amalfi-coast-walking#Your holiday includes">Your holiday includes</a> | <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/amalfi-coast-walking#Hotels">Hotels</a>| <a href="https://www.inghams.co.uk/destinations/tours-multi-centres/tours-multi-centres-in-italy/amalfi-coast-walking#Departure dates">Departure dates</a></h2>
